title: Minecraft Live 2021: Introducing new mobs!
author: Minecraft
description: We have three new mobs for you to vote for during this year’s Minecraft Live! Join Tiny Vu, Tiny Agnes, and Tiny Jens for an introduction to the – wait, where did Tiny Agnes go?? Hopefully Tiny Jens will find her before the show starts on October 16 at noon EDT!
